<section class="turn" id="the-turn">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="turn__inner reveal">
      <p class="overline">The Turn</p>
      <hr class="fire-rule" />
      <h2 class="display turn__heading">
        I left early.<br/><em>It was enough.</em>
      </h2>
      <div class="turn__body">
        <p>
          In the military, I got married. I got pregnant. And at four years of service — 
          with everything still ahead of me in uniform — I made the hardest decision 
          of my life and chose a different path.
        </p>
        <p>
          For years, I carried the weight of that choice like a wound. The shame of 
          leaving early. The grief of an identity I'd poured myself into. The question 
          that wouldn't quiet itself: <em>What would I have become?</em>
        </p>
        <p>
          But time — and honest reckoning — has a way of rewriting the story. I didn't 
          abandon my service. I completed it on my own terms. And every skill I built, 
          every crew I led, every mission I owned, every standard I upheld — all of it 
          came with me.
        </p>
        <p>
          I have since put my life in full perspective. The shame is gone. 
          What I carried out of that chapter is worth more than what I left behind.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.turn {
  padding-block: var(--section-pad);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--coal) 0%, var(--ash) 100%);
  position: relative;
}
.turn::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--crimson), transparent);
}
.turn__inner {
  max-width: 700px;
}
.turn__heading {
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.turn__heading em {
  color: var(--flame);
  font-style: italic;
}
.turn__body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.4rem;
  color: var(--bone);
  opacity: 0.85;
}
.turn__body em {
  color: var(--amber);
  font-style: italic;
}
</style>
